values: OK, so I started my LJ for a new PC in the upcoming chronicle: ShadeChronicles ENJOY!

Enzo stared into the small screen quietly crossing himself.  Miami, it had been a disaster, and now this modern masquerade was shattered.  

Kindred were common knowledge; the years of effort spent making them a legend had failed.  The world knew they were real.  Would the young ones understand?  Could they?  This is where it all began, hunters stalking the night, the common man armed with superstitious remedies and the church seeking the hunters.

He could hear Francesca in the kitchen and he silently prayed.  She might be safe; whatever she was, she was not a creature of the night.  He looked into the mirror and sighed, yes he looked human, he never hunted, his life went by quietly, but the sun would give him away.  

He sighed; God never seemed to make it easy.

OK Just wanted to let everyone know that Ms. Jones has an LJ. You may recall her as the scary ghoul of Jack's that got poached by Bryce. At anyrate she's back with all her scary fetishclad Brujahness so I wanted to let folks know: msjones_cam

But all this unadulterated goodness, which I'll add has been some phenomenal roleplay, needed to be cut with some old fashioned evil. The link is: mementomorix
